The is one condition condition (likely edge case) I'm aware of when using Option 2. Basically if a Web Component defines only a getter and not a setter then both Preact and Vue 3 break, but the current version of React doesn't (at least React 16 and 17). 

**Condition that would cause an error if using Option 2 but will work with React 16 and 17**
```js
